description: The Lockheed AT-33A Shooting Star is a close-air-support version of the T-33A trainer. It has a single engine and unswept wings. It is armed with two .50 cal machine guns and has provision for under-wing stores.
loadnotes: Either stations 2 and 3 or stations 5 to 8 can be used.
Stations 5 to 8 can each carry two RK.
